headline: KEYCORP ANNOUNCES SHARE REPURCHASE PROGRAM
summary: KeyCorp (NYSE: KEY) today announced that its Board of Directors has authorized a share repurchase program pursuant to which KeyCorp may purchase up to $1.0 billion of KeyCorp common shares, in the open market or in privately negotiated transactions.
